path.aria-label: PlayStation® Vita cannot open this website

g.aria-label:
We regret to inform you that the official AGRF website uses technologies that the PlayStation® Vita console's web browser does not support.
If we were to let you view our website, it would look broken. Our website looks good on mobile and great on desktop, though!
You may also view our legacy website by clicking the button below. This will use a cookie so we can remember this decision.
